<p>Advanced Race Guide pg. 98 <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-1" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-1" aria-label="Back to reference C-1">↩</InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-2" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-2" aria-label="Back to reference C-2">↩<sup>2</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-3" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-3" aria-label="Back to reference C-3">↩<sup>3</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-4" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-4" aria-label="Back to reference C-4">↩<sup>4</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-5" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-5" aria-label="Back to reference C-5">↩<sup>5</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-6" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-6" aria-label="Back to reference C-6">↩<sup>6</sup></InnerLink> <InnerLink id="backlink-race-dhampir-ref-C-7" data-hash-target to="race-dhampir-ref-C-7" aria-label="Back to reference C-7">↩<sup>7</sup></InnerLink></p>
